The paper proposes a neural network architecture based on LSTM for time series regression problem of predicting sea surface temperature. This falls under the domain of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE. The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for image processing, which falls under the sub-category cs.CV. Finally, the paper discusses the online updated characteristics of the model, which could be related to the sub-category cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
